data.description: This 3 bedroom, 3 bath, 2281 sqft home is more than just a place to live.  This home is strategically centrally placed for convenience, with easy access to schools, shopping, and all that this city has to offer.  Enjoy breathtaking mountain views from various vantage points. The open kitchen, features a spacious island, sleek stainless steel appliances, and ample counter space, making it a perfect hub for culinary delights and gatherings. The primary bedroom has an attached bath and hardwood floors, adding warmth and timeless charm to every living space. The other two spacious bedrooms have hardwood flooring and natural light filtering in. On the upper level you will also find a full bath. The lower level features a family room with a wood-burning fireplace, the ideal setting as the seasons change. The lower level has a 1/2 bath for convenience.The covered patio and backyard is tailor-made and perfect for entertaining. Mature trees surround the property, providing shade, privacy, and a sense of connection to nature right outside your door. Don't miss your chance to experience this exceptional property!
